# Client-side
<client>
<server>
http
</server>

<name>
Check if %{stderr} and %{stdout} switch between stdout and stderr.
</name>
<command>
http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/%TESTNUMBER --silent --write-out 'line1%{stderr}line2%{stdout}line3'
</command>
</client>

